quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  33,63,"Yim…ìe sirkoo…ìe …ìen hino lanndo maa an Nulaa…óo, lanndal ≈ãi√±ugol e fennugol, Alyahuuuda'en kadi no lanndo maa fii Darngal, ko honnde tuma? Maakan …ìee: Anndal daragol Darngal, ko ka Alla woni, mi alanaa …óum ganndal. E ko anndin maa an Nulaa…óo, wonnde no hasii hara Darngal ngal …ìadike?"
  33,64,"Pellet, Alla wo…ó…óintinii heefer…ìe …ìen e yurmeende Makko, O hebilanii …ìe kadi √ëalnde Darngal, Yiite dul…ìoowe, sabbitiinge …ìe."
  33,65,"Ko …ìe luttoo…ìe e lepte ngen Yiite hebilanaa …ìe nge poomaa. ∆Åe he…ìataa ton gi…óo nafoowo …ìe, wanaa ballo du√±anoowo …ìe lepte magge."
  33,66,"√ëalnde Darngal, geece ma…ì…ìe …óen waylitete ka Yiite Jahannama, …ìe wi'oya tuma ninse e hayrere tii…ói : Ee jalla amen, e nguurndam amen aduna! Hara men …óoftorino Alla wa…óugol ko O yamirniri men, wo…ó…óitoo e ko O ha…ói men, men …óoftii Nulaa…óo on e ko o addi kon immorde ka Joomi makko!"
  33,67,"∆Åe ardoya e hujjaaji meerente, …ìe wi'a: Joomi amen, menen men …óofti hooree…ìe amen e maw…ìe amen, …ìe majjini men e laawol focciingol ngol."
  33,68,"Joomi amen, defu …ìee hooree…ìe e maw…ìe majjin…ìe min laawol focciingol ngol, cowanlle …ói…ói e ko wa…óan-…óaa men kon ka lepte, sabu ko …ìe majjinir men kon, hu…óaa…ìe kadi kuddi mawnudi."
  33,69,"Ko onon yo …ìen gom…óim…ìe Alla, …ìe golliri ko O sar'inani …ìe kon, wata on lorru Nulaa…óo mon on, haa wa'on wa …ìen lorrunoo…ìe Muusaa, wano ko …ìe aybinirnoo mo e …ìanndu makko, kono Alla wo…ó…óini mo e ko …ìe wi'i kon. ∆Åanngani …ìe wonnde himo hisi e …óum, tawde Muusaa wonii teddu…óo ka Alla, …óa…ì- …ìal makko ruttetaake, faale makko bonnitetaake."
  33,70,"Ko onon yo …ìen gom…óim…ìe Alla, …ìe gollitiri ko O sar'inani …ìe kon, huliree Alla …óoftagol yamirooje Makko, e wo…ó…óitagol ha…óaa…ói Makko, wowlon konngol goonga, hawrungol e sawaaba."
  33,71,"Si on hulii Alla, on wowlii konngol peewngol, O mo∆¥∆¥inanay on golle mon, O ja…ìana on …óe, O yawtana on junubaaji mon, hara O nanngitirtaa on …ói. Kala …óoftii…óo Alla e Nulaa…óo Makko on, haray o maliraama maloore mawnde, nde sugu mun alaa, nden woni malireede welayee Alla e naatugol Aljanna."
  33,72,"Men wee…ìitii pawe sar'ia …óin, e kala ko reenetee, immorde e jawle e gunndooji, Men wee…ìiti …óum e dow kammuuli …óin, e leydi ndin e pelle …óen, kono …ói ha…óitii ronndagol …ói, …ói huli battane muu…óum. Ne…ó…óo on kan ronndii…ói; tawde pellet, o wonii too√±oowo hoore-mun, majjaa…óo battane ronndagol …óum."
  33,73,"Alla hoddirii nde ne…ó…óo on ronndora hoolaare nden, fii no O leptira naafiqee…ìe wor…ìe …ìen e naafaqee…ìe rew…ìe …ìen, e sirkoo…ìe wor…ìe …ìen e sirkoo…ìe rew…ìe …ìen, fii naafiqaaku ma…ì…ìe e sirku ma…ì…ìe on, e fii no Alla ja…ìirana gom…óim…ìe wor…ìe …ìen e gom…óim…ìe rew…ìe mo∆¥∆¥im…ìe ronndagol hoolaare kaliifuuji sar'ia on. Alla siforii Hafranoowo kala tuubu…óo e jeyaa…ìe Makko …ìen, Hinnotoo…óo …ìe."